Houston Lighting Power Co unit Houston Industries Inc redeem May 4 par plus accrue 140 mln dlrs mortgage bonds. The utility expect redemption save nearly mln dlrs annually expenses. Houston Lighting recently exchange 390 mln dlrs coupon bond nine pct bond save 11 mln dlrs annual costs. Houston Lighting plan buy outstanding 11-1/4 pct bond 2009 12 due 2010 12-3/8s 2013 11-5/8s due 2015 10-1/8s 2004. Reuter 